全球多地现新冠病毒社区传播迹象，尚未达到旅游警示标准。
There are signs of community transmission of the new crown virus in many parts of the world and travel alert standards have not yet been met.
金焱。
Yan, Jin.
财经杂志                      。
Financial magazine.
