《财经》杂志官方微信。
An official letter from Caijing magazine.
《财经》杂志由中国证券市场研究中心主办，1998年创刊，秉承“独立、独家、独到”的新闻理念，以权威性、公正性、专业性报道见长，是政经学界决策者、研究者、管理者的必读刊物。
"Caijing" magazine, sponsored by the China Securities Market Research Center, was founded in 1998, upholding the news concept of "independence, exclusivity and originality," and providing authoritative, impartial and professional reports.
。
.
韩国发生新冠肺炎超级传播事件，美国担忧日本、新加坡、韩国、泰国及越南等国及台湾地区出现社区传播文|《财经》特派记者金焱发自华盛顿编辑 |苏琦当地时间2月20日，美国疾病控制与预防中心(CDC)在网站上指出，多国和地区出现新冠病毒的社区传播迹象。
The United States is concerned about the emergence of community-based transmission in countries such as Japan, Singapore, South Korea, Thailand and Vietnam, as well as Taiwan. Yan Jin, a reporter with Caijing, is at least twice as likely to spread the virus as the U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) said on its Web site.
这一信息出现在该网针对2019新冠病毒的旅游相关信息中，虽然美国CDC认定包括日本、新加坡、韩国、泰国及越南、中国台湾等地已出现明显的传播，但尚未达到旅游警示的标准。
This information appears in the Network's travel-related information on the 2019 new crown virus, although the United States CDC has found significant spread in places including Japan, Singapore, South Korea, Thailand and Vietnam, as well as Taiwan, China, but has yet to meet the criteria for travel alerts.
社区传播的槛美国CDC解释称，所谓“社区传播”意味着出现感染病毒的案例，但部分个案有感染地点、感染途径不明等状况。
Community-spread sill The U.S. CDC said the so-called "community transmission" meant there had been cases of infection, but in some cases the location and route of infection were unknown.
美国CDC对香港地区发出的旅游警示为最低一级的“观察（Watch）”，未建议取消或延后访问香港行程，但提醒旅客避免接触患者，并要经常洗手或使用酒精搓手液。
The CDC's travel alert for Hong Kong is the lowest level of "Watch." It does not recommend canceling or postponing visits to Hong Kong, but advises travellers to avoid contact with patients and to wash hands regularly or use alcohol-based hand rub.
与此同时，韩国政府2月20日宣布，新冠病毒已突破该国的防疫网，出现社区感染扩散的迹象。
Meanwhile, South Korea's government announced on February 20 that the new crown virus has broken through the country's epidemic prevention network, showing signs of spreading infection in the community.
韩国大邱更是发生了新冠肺炎超级传播事件，一名61岁女性成为超级传播者。
South Korea's Daegu case of the New Crown Pneumonia super-transmission, a 61-year-old woman became a super communicator.
大邱当地政府敦促其250万居民待在家中。
Daegu's local government has urged its 2.5 million residents to stay at home.
大邱是位于韩国东南部除首尔、釜山、仁川之外的韩国第四大城市，人口密度2818人/平方公里。
Daegu is South Korea's fourth largest city in southeast Korea, excluding Seoul, Busan and Incheon, with a population density of 2,818 people per square kilometer.
根据最新统计，韩国20日下午新增22例新冠肺炎病例，使其确诊病例总数达到104例。
According to the latest statistics, South Korea on the afternoon of 20 new cases of new crown pneumonia, bringing the total number of confirmed cases to 104.
韩国也出现了首例死亡案例。
South Korea also has its first case of death.
日本已有数百人被确诊感染了新冠病毒，三人死亡。
Hundreds of people in Japan have been diagnosed with the new crown virus and three have died.
停靠在横滨大黑港口的钻石公主号游轮更因为确诊人数的高速增加吸引了全球的关注。
The cruise ship The Princess Diamond, docked at Yokohama Black Harbor, attracted global attention for its rapid increase in the number of people diagnosed.
世卫组织总干事谭德塞2月18日在日内瓦举行的有关2019冠状病毒疫情媒体通报会上指出，在此前的24小时里，中国境外共出现110起新病例，其中99起发生在钻石公主号游轮上。
Speaking at a media briefing on the 2019 coronavirus outbreak in Geneva on February 18, WHO Director-General Thant said that in the previous 24 hours, there had been 110 new cases outside China, 99 of which occurred on board the MV Princess Diamond.
、因陆续发生感染源不明个案，早在2月17日日本就被认为至少已出现隐性社区传播。
As early as February 17, at least hidden community transmission was thought to have occurred in Japan due to the continued occurrence of unknown sources of infection.
2月19日0—24时，中国国家卫健委收到港澳台地区通报确诊病例99例：中国香港特别行政区65例(出院5例，死亡2例)，中国澳门特别行政区10例(出院6例)，中国台湾地区24例(出院2例，死亡1例)。
On February 19, between 0000 and 2400 hours, the Chinese National Fitness and Health Commission received notification of 99 confirmed cases in Hong Kong, Macao and Taiwan: 65 cases in the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region of China (5 cases of discharge and 2 cases of death), 10 cases in the Macao Special Administrative Region of China (6 cases of discharge) and 24 cases in Taiwan region of China (2 cases of discharge and 1 case of death).
中国台湾地区确诊的24例中有1例感染源不明。
The source of infection is unknown in 1 of the 24 cases diagnosed in Taiwan.
中国台湾地区相关部门负责人陈时中1月16日公布台湾地区首例冠状病毒死亡个案，在记者会上被问到是否代表台湾出现社区感染时，陈时中回答：“可以这么说”，引发哗然。
Chen Shizhong, the head of Taiwan's Taiwan province's first case of coronavirus-related death, was shocked when asked at a press conference whether the case represents a community infection in Taiwan.
当晚他改口只是“社区内零星个案”。
That night he switched to "sporadic cases in the community."
1月19日深夜，台湾地区相关部门书面公布第24例确诊妇人，两年无旅游史，感染源不明，再次引发台湾地区是否发生社区传播的质疑。
Late last night on January 19, Taiwan authorities announced in writing the 24th confirmed case of a woman with no travel history for two years.
新加坡政府此前已追踪出本地的数个感染集群，但新加坡政府也未出面承认新冠病毒已在该国出现“广泛的社区传播”。
The Singapore government has previously traced several local infection clusters, but it has not acknowledged that the virus has "spread widely in the community."
意大利前环境部长科拉多-克利尼(Corrado Clini)对《财经》记者指出，情况已经表明，新型冠状病毒带来的挑战要求在全球范围内采取协调一致的行动，而不是把中国隔离出去。
Corrado Clini, Italy's former environment minister, told Caijing that the challenge posed by the new coronavirus had been shown to require concerted global action, not China's isolation.
新型冠状病毒戏剧性的发展也可能会扭转“去全球化”和经济脱钩的趋势。
The dramatic development of the new coronavirus could also reverse the trend of "de-globalisation" and economic decoupling.
韩国大邱疫情样本外界也注意到，最近中国疫情出现好转。
South Korea Daegu outbreak sample outside also noted that the recent outbreak of China has improved.
2月19日0-24时，中国除湖北以外地区新增确诊病例45例，连续16日下降。
From 0 to 24 p.m. on February 19, 45 new cases were diagnosed in China, down from Hubei province for 16 consecutive days.
但韩国近日新型冠状病毒感染激增，加剧了人们的担忧。
But concerns have been heightened by a surge in new coronavirus infections in South Korea.
韩国基准股指韩国综合指数2月20日下跌0.7%，对疫情的担忧促使投资者逃离高风险资产。
South Korea's benchmark stock index, the South Korean composite index, fell 0.7% Feb. 20, as concerns about the outbreak prompted investors to flee risky assets.
韩国东南部城市大邱一夜之间成为韩国的重灾区。
South Korea's southeastern city of Daegu overnight became a major disaster area.
韩国相关部门认为，新冠病毒感染扩散蔓延已呈现极其严重的地步。
South Korean authorities believe that the spread of the new crown virus infection has become extremely serious.
韩国总统文在寅与中国国家主席习近平通电话，希望中国分析抗疫情的临床经验。
South Korean President Wen Jieyin spoke by telephone with Chinese President Xi Jinping, hoping that China would analyse its clinical experience in fighting the epidemic.
韩国2月20日证实该国首例新冠病毒感染者死亡病例，并报告了22例新病例。
South Korea confirmed its first case of human death and reported 22 new cases on February 20.
韩国的疾病防控中心、中央防疫对策本部称，这名韩国男性今年63岁，在庆尚北道清道郡一家医院因精神分裂症住院多年，最近出现肺炎症状。
South Korea's Centers for Disease Control and Prevention and the Central Prevention and Control Department said the 63-year-old South Korean man has recently developed symptoms of pneumonia after years of hospitalization for schizophrenia at a Ching Tao hospital in Gyeongshan North Province.
卫生部门在这名患者死亡后对其进行病毒检测结果为阳性。
Health authorities tested positive for the virus after the patient's death.
韩国半导体大厂海力士(SK Hynix Inc.)因有新进员工疑似感染新冠病毒，其余800多名员工则被要求返家隔离。
At SK Hynix Inc., a major semiconductor maker, more than 800 workers were ordered to return home to quarantine after new employees were suspected of contracting the virus.
韩国新的感染区域集中在大邱市的一座教堂，这里是大邱教会的教徒做礼拜之地。
New infections are concentrated in a church in Daegu, where Daegu church members worship.
有报道称韩国第31例确诊患者、61岁的韩国妇女曾在2月9日和2月16日先后两次前往“新天地”大邱教会做礼拜，但最近没有出国旅行史，这名患者2月18日确诊感染了冠状病毒肺炎。
South Korea's 31st confirmed patient, a 61-year-old South Korean woman, was reported to have visited the Taegu Church in Xintiandi on February 9 and February 16, but did not travel abroad recently. The patient was diagnosed with coronavirus pneumonia on February 18.
在过去几天韩国确诊的73例病例中，有49位患者去过这名韩国妇女到过的新天地教会，或者跟这个确诊病患在其他地方接触过。
Of the 73 cases diagnosed in South Korea in the past few days, 49 patients have visited the New World Church where the South Korean woman has been, or have been in contact with, the confirmed patient elsewhere.
新天地教会在韩国有大约20万信徒，与其关联的74处教堂已经全部关闭。
The Church of Xintiandi has about 200,000 members in South Korea, and all 74 churches affiliated with it have been closed.
大邱教堂有大约8000名信徒。
Daegu has about 8,000 members.
2月20日，韩国中央防疫对策本部本部长郑银敬表示，已从“新天地”大邱教会获取了与第31例患者一起进行礼拜的1001名教徒的名单，正在对这些人员采取居家隔离措施，并通过电话确认这些人员是否出现症状。
On February 20, Zheng Yingjing, minister of the Central Preventive Measures Ministry, said the 1,001 people who had attended services with the 31st case had been taken from the Daegu Church in Xintiandi, and were being isolated from their homes and confirmed by telephone if they had symptoms.
这次超级传播事件也迫使当地250万居民待在家中。
The supertransmission has also forced 2.5 million residents to stay at home.
韩国传染病专家认为，新冠病毒肺炎死亡率高于A型流感，低于中东呼吸症候群(MERS)。
South Korean infectious disease experts believe the death rate from Newcastle virus pneumonia is higher than influenza A, lower than the Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS).
郑银敬称，在庆尚北道清道郡和大邱市出现的确诊病例多与“新天地”教会有关联，教徒的家属等很多人存在感染风险，政府呼吁克制在封闭的环境下长时间进行的集体活动。
Zheng Yin-kwong said many of the confirmed cases in Qinghai and Daegu cities in the northern province of Gyeongshan were linked to the Xintiandi church, where many people, including their families, were at risk of infection, and called for restraint in long-term group activities in closed environments.
大邱市政府发布的数据表明，截至20日当天上午，“新天地”大邱教会1001名教徒中回答有症状的人有90人，回答没有出现症状的人有515人，其余396人尚未取得联系。
As of the morning of the 20th, 90 of the 1,001 Taegu clergy in Xintiandi had answered symptoms, 515 had not, and the remaining 396 had not, according to data released by the city government.
大邱市市市长权泳臻（Kwon Young-jin）担心感染人数增加可能会让该市医疗卫生系统不堪重负，并呼吁中央政府提供紧急驰援。
Kwon Young-jin, the mayor of Daegu, worried that the rising number of infections could overwhelm the city's health-care system, and called on the central government to provide emergency assistance.
他说：“旨在阻断病毒从中国进入和防止扩散的国家隔离努力，不足以防止病毒在当地社区传播。
National isolation efforts aimed at stopping the virus from entering China and preventing its spread are not enough to prevent the virus from spreading in local communities, he said.
